// AS3 linkage class `ScreenPickATeamAlt` is the openfl-swf generated library symbol `Screen_pickATeam_alt` (the SWF symbol's
// library name was snake/lowerCamel; openfl names the class from it, not the AS3 linkage). Alias the
// two so `new ScreenPickATeamAlt()` constructs the real clip (with its named child instances), not an empty stub.
typedef ScreenPickATeamAlt = Screen_pickATeam_alt;
